name: Trap-Jaw Dobsonfly
text:
1 Tuner monster + 1 non-Tuner Insect monster
If this card is Synchro Summoned: You can add 1 "Trap-Jaw'' Spell/Trap from your Deck to your hand. If this card is sent from the field to the GY: You can Special Summon 1 "Trap-Jaw" monster from your hand. You can only activate each effect of "Trap-Jaw Dobsonfly" once per turn.
